9eae422c-7d5a-4c99-89c2-c31c9843e98b.title: Tracker gnome 1
9eae422c-7d5a-4c99-89c2-c31c9843e98b.text:
I can't talk now. Can't you see we're trying to win a
battle here?

0a09624d-161d-4613-9cc6-e8f657b726c2.title: <player>
0a09624d-161d-4613-9cc6-e8f657b726c2.text:
Do you know the coordinates of the Khazard
stronghold?

1506f325-42d4-46d0-8929-ca4f26df65fe.title: Tracker gnome 1
1506f325-42d4-46d0-8929-ca4f26df65fe.text: I managed to get one, although it wasn't easy.

1b32d423-cf68-4fa2-880b-715309ba54a6.text: The gnome tells you the height coordinate.

bac21711-0953-4be9-906a-f7888534fdb3.title: Tracker gnome 1
bac21711-0953-4be9-906a-f7888534fdb3.text:
The other two tracker gnomes should have the other
coordinates if they're still alive.

9fe77cae-8a28-40c3-af20-9f83bed89630.title: Tracker gnome 1
9fe77cae-8a28-40c3-af20-9f83bed89630.text:
Well done, you've broken down their defences. This
battle must be ours.

28651fee-b9b3-4ce1-ac18-e7d32c294428.title: Tracker gnome 1
28651fee-b9b3-4ce1-ac18-e7d32c294428.text:
Now we have the orb I'm much better. They won't
stand a chance without it.

01e10012-12b0-43de-ae87-f267350998bb.title: Tracker gnome 1
01e10012-12b0-43de-ae87-f267350998bb.text:
When will this battle end? I feel like I've been fighting
forever.
